Q4. You want to enable authentication for your App Service using Azure Active Directory without modifying your application code.

👉 What should you use?

⸻

Options:

A) Implement custom JWT authentication
B) Azure AD B2C SDK
C) App Service Authentication (Easy Auth)
D) API Management

Answer - C)

App Service Authentication (Easy Auth) lets you:
	•	Enable login (Azure AD, Google, etc.)
	•	Without writing any code
	•	Handled at the platform level (before request hits your app)
